<div dir="ltr"><span id="docs-internal-guid-c3645293-cc69-5189-ee23-cd54565b39a0"><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.15;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt"><span style="font-size:15px;font-family:Arial;color:rgb(0,0,0);vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;background-color:transparent">Happy New Year Everyone!</span></p><br><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.15;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt"><span style="font-size:15px;font-family:Arial;color:rgb(0,0,0);vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;background-color:transparent">We just released another beta version of Ushahidi v3. This is </span><span style="font-size:15px;font-family:Arial;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;background-color:transparent">milestone 3 of 3 </span><span style="font-size:15px;font-family:Arial;color:rgb(0,0,0);vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;background-color:transparent">towards the first non-beta release</span><span style="font-size:15px;font-family:Arial;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;background-color:transparent">! </span><span style="font-size:15px;font-family:Arial;color:rgb(0,0,0);vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;background-color:transparent">The next release will be a sprint in this milestone series, released two weeks from now. </span></p><h2 dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.15;margin-top:10pt;margin-bottom:0pt"><span style="font-size:17px;font-family:&#39;Trebuchet MS&#39;;color:rgb(0,0,0);vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;background-color:transparent">What’s new with V3.0.0-beta.12?</span></h2><br><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.15;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt"><span style="font-size:15px;font-family:Arial;color:rgb(0,0,0);vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;background-color:transparent">Here’s what you can expect from this release:-</span></p><br><br><ul style="margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt"><li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type:d